comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) makes marginal contact with Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) arm that does not affect his ability to grab the rebound.
Randle (ORL) legally contests Schroder's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) reaches out and marginal contact occurs with Bacon's (ORL) body as he begins his upward shooting motion during the jump shot attempt.
Randle (ORL) places two hands on Schroder (LAL) and the contact affects his SQBR.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) makes contact to Bacon's (ORL) body during the drive that affects his SQBR.
Carter Jr. (ORL) does not dislodge Caldwell-Pope (LAL) as he approaches him during the off-ball screen. The contact that occurs is marginal and he does not move through his space.
Carter Jr. (ORL) legally contests Harrell's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) and Carter Jr. (ORL) make incidental contact when Carter Jr. begins to run up the floor after the made dunk.
Bacon (ORL) maintains a legal guarding during Schroder's (LAL) driving shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) reaches in and makes contact with the ball after Harrell (LAL) gathers the rebound.
Kuzma (LAL) steps on the sideline after retrieving the loose ball.
